                                <para>Displaced Part</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry></entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Slotted Dowel Pin 25.4 mm (1.0 inch) in length. Used on engines with Serial Number
                                    505017 and Below.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>19 328 R1</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
